name: The C h o n k
description:
Loudly inspired by a picture of Cher I saw.
If you know me. You know I use the black cat as a persona.

Secret between me and whoever read my description : I'm a dog person.
The black cat help me separate my regular self from the NFT side of me.

Every time I'd log in, I'd say to myself "It is I, the cat" because it makes
me chuckle and help get into the character better.
